# Baselines Before Agent

Apply when editing baselines, agent logic, evaluation, or experiment configs.

## Ordering Constraint
- Do not add agent complexity before runnable baselines exist and are evaluated.

## Required Baselines
- rule baseline
- tabular ML baseline
- single-pass LLM baseline
- simple RAG baseline

## Shared Contract
- All systems must emit the same final strict JSON schema.
- No free-form benchmark outputs.
- Evaluation must score workflow behavior, not only final prediction quality.

## New Agent Feature Gate
Every new agent feature must state:
- which benchmark failure mode it addresses
- which baseline it should beat
- which metric should show gain
- which ablation isolates its contribution
